======
bukkit
======

:Author:
    Keith Gaughan (http://stereochro.me)

:Repo:
    https://github.com/kgaughan/bukkit


A token bucket library.

.. image:: https://secure.travis-ci.org/kgaughan/bukkit.png?branch=master
   :width: 89px
   :height: 13px
   :target: http://travis-ci.org/kgaughan/bukkit


Overview
========

*bukkit* is a small library to control resource consumption over time using
`token bucket algorithm`_. It provides both a standalone class that implements
the token bucket algorithm and a class for managing a keyed collection of
token buckets.


.. _token bucket algorithm: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Token_bucket
